N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 195.6 - Use of trade or corporate name

State Regulations

No licensee or applicant may use a trade or corporate name
which, in the opinion of the Department of State, is so similar to the trade
name or corporate name of any licensee that confusion to the public will result
therefrom. Notes
